# YQuantum dashboard styling

For any UI (web, dashboards, charts, notebooks rendered as HTML), follow **`DESIGN_SYSTEM_FOR_AGENTS.md`** at the repo root: Travelers red / Yale blue / platform blue tokens, light gray app shell, report-like tables, algorithm colors (QAOA `#0066CC`, DQI `#00356B`, classical `#2D8C3C`).

Do not introduce unrelated palettes or decorative “startup” styling. If the challenge materials repo is cloned locally, use `Travelers/docs/01_insurance_bundling.html` and `06_scaling.html` as reference implementations; otherwise rely on the token table and rules in the design brief.
